    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个健康科技系统的数据流图。核心是两个模块：LabAnalyzer负责实验室分析，PatientRecords管理患者档案。这两个模块之间有直接的数据交换。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。LabAnalyzer和PatientRecords是左右排列还是上下排列？另外，它们之间的连线是单向还是双向的数据流？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "左右排列吧，从左到右表示分析结果流向档案系统。连线不用箭头，简单的一条线表示关联关系就行，因为实际上数据是双向同步的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画好了。左边是HealthTech_LabAnalyzer节点，右边是HealthTech_PatientRecords节点，中间用一条无向线连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，节点名称显示得不太对。LabAnalyzer那边显示成了log6，PatientRecords显示成了log7，这个内部标识不应该暴露出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "log6",
        "log7"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "抱歉，这是Mermaid的语法问题。log6和log7是我用的内部节点ID，但显示文本应该是括号里的HealthTech_LabAnalyzer和HealthTech_PatientRecords。您看到的是代码视图还是渲染图？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "log6",
        "log7",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "哦，渲染图是对的，显示的是完整名称。那就没问题了。log6和log7作为内部ID可以接受，只要最终呈现给用户的是规范的业务名称就行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "log6",
        "log7",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
